    Richard Valente, Nicola Wharton,
    Jordan O'Leary, Melissa Shabinsky

    • Edit
    • Duplicate
    • Remove

    Like the way that a lot of new concepts start, we couldn't find a place in Ottawa where we could find raw, cold pressed juices, healthy smoothies, salads and plant-based snacks and foods that we could grab on the go but where we could also get a great organic coffee and teas, so we decided to build it on our own - a brand new concept to Ottawa - the first ever juicery and espresso bar.


    Our vision was to create a wellness destination with a fun, energetic vibe. With our combined expertise in restaurants, coffee houses, design, decor and branding, we thought we could make something really special here in our city.

    Raw Reboot Cleanse guide

      Pre-Cleanse

      We recommend starting to pre-cleanse at least 2-3 days prior to starting your juice cleanse. Gradually cut out meat, dairy, processed sugar, gluten, alcohol, and caffeine. By the day before you start juice cleansing, you should be eating nothing but a clean, plant-based diet.

      • Edit
      • Duplicate
      • Remove
      • Edit
      • Duplicate
      • Remove
      • Edit
      • Duplicate
      • Remove

      The Program

      Enjoy a juice every 2-3 hours. Feel free to drink as much water and herbal teas between juices as you would like. Drink juices in order from 1 to 6 and an elixir for an extra boost.

      • Edit
      • Duplicate
      • Remove
      • Edit
      • Duplicate
      • Remove
      • Edit
      • Duplicate
      • Remove

      Post Cleanse

      Just like the pre-cleanse, start to introduce foods back into your diet the same way you eliminated them. Maybe start with some smoothies and soups the first day off juicing and introduce light meals, as you feel best.
